    {
      "handle": "story-q52jw1no",
      "url": "https://grabzi.ae/pages/story/story-q52jw1no",
      "title": "story-q52jw1no\n – GRABZI",
      "text": "Our Story\nGRABZI started with a dream, but not the usual kind.\nIt began with an idea for a burger concept called WKND150, available only on weekends and serving just 150 burgers a day. Simple, limited, and special. However, turning that idea into reality required many resources such as staff, equipment, gas, a large kitchen, and a big budget.\nSo I decided to start smarter.\nOne day, I noticed a V60 coffee kit at home, and the idea naturally shifted from burgers to coffee. The concept stayed the same: limited quantities, strong identity, and a unique experience, but in a lighter, faster, and cooler form\nOne style. One vibe. 150 cups a day.\nWhen it’s sold out, it’s gone.\nSo grab it before it’s gone. GRABZI.",
      "links": []
    },
